# stow should link ONLY statusline-pace.py from this package.
#
# settings.json is COPY-managed by ./install, not stowed: Claude Code atomically
# rewrites ~/.claude/settings.json (temp file + rename) on /model, /config, etc.,
# which would detach a stow symlink — and symlinked settings also trip permission-
# recognition failures + slow startups (anthropics/claude-code#3575, #40857).
# README.md is documentation.
#
# NOTE: defining this file replaces stow's built-in default ignore list, so the
# README pattern must be repeated here.
settings\.json
README.*
